-magazine/blog/li-songsong-at-pace-london,455,BAR.html\">Li Songsong at Pace London – Royal Academy of Arts blog\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://artdaily.com/news/65174/Exhibition-of-new-paintings-by-the-Chinese-artist-Li-Songsong-opens-at-Pace-London#.UnQiPFND6So\">Exhibition of new paintings by the Chinese artist Li Songsong opens at Pace London – Art Daily</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/li-songsong-we-have-betrayed-the-revolution-pace/","prefix":"1 November 2013"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Li Songsong: We Have Betrayed the Revolution, Pace Gallery (until Nov 9)","category":"exhibits","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/d8bef26a041c1afbfd68bc0d7051df49/47498/li-songsong1_anu7bg.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"b6415c02-57f6-5889-8910-a05deb06efca","html":"<p>Article by <strong>Tuesday Gutierrez</strong>. Former digital marketing manager for the London 2012 Festival, the largest UK festival ever staged. This is her blog about contemporary art, design, film, photography and all that move her soul.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/li-songsong-we-have-betrayed-the-revolution-pace/","prev":{"id":"1bb8439b-8129-571d-95f2-110c86823025","fields":{"slug":"/ten-royal-british-society-of-sculptors-bursary-award-winners-2013/","prefix":"16 October 2013","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ten Royal British Society of Sculptors Bursary Award Winners 2013","category":"exhibits"}},"next":{"id":"7551bf64-6979-5058-8c67-a1942b7ecbc3","fields":{"slug":"/bloggers-event-castiliogne-the-lost-genius-queens-gallery-royal-collection/","prefix":"4 November 2013","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Blogger's Event on Castiliogne: the Lost Genius - Queen's Gallery, Royal Collection","category":"exhibits"}},"source":"posts"}}}